    static final class RocksDBKeyedStateBackend.MergeIterator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.AutoCloseable
    Wraps a RocksDB iterator to cache it's current key and assign an id for the key/value state to the iterator. Used by #MergeIterator.
